  "explanation_html": "<div class=\"lc-section\"><h3 style=\"margin:0 0 12px 0;color:var(--lc-primary);\">🎯 題目重新框架</h3><p style=\"line-height:1.6;\">給你一個 <code>n × n</code> 的二維整數矩陣，請將整個矩陣<strong>順時針旋轉 90 度</strong>，且必須<strong>就地（in-place）</strong>完成——不能另外建立一個同樣大小的新矩陣來存放結果。</p><p style=\"line-height:1.6;\">可以把矩陣想像成一張圖片的像素格：旋轉後，最左欄的像素整列移到最上排，最下排的像素整列移到最左欄，依此類推。</p><div style=\"background:rgba(91,141,239,0.08);padding:12px;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;border-left:3px solid var(--lc-primary);\"><strong>📌 範例：</strong><br><code>matrix = [[1,2,3],[4,5,6],[7,8,9]]</code><br>→ 旋轉後：<code>[[7,4,1],[8,5,2],[9,6,3]]</code></div><svg viewBox=\"0 0 600 200\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:8px 0;\"><text x=\"95\" y=\"16\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-muted)\" font-size=\"12\">輸入</text><rect x=\"10\" y=\"22\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"rgba(91,141,239,0.18)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><rect x=\"60\" y=\"22\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"rgba(91,141,239,0.12)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><rect x=\"110\" y=\"22\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"rgba(91,141,239,0.06)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><rect x=\"10\" y=\"72\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"rgba(91,141,239,0.18)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><rect x=\"60\" y=\"72\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"rgba(91,141,239,0.12)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><rect x=\"110\" y=\"72\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"rgba(91,141,239,0.06)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><rect x=\"10\" y=\"122\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"rgba(91,141,239,0.18)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><rect x=\"60\" y=\"122\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"rgba(91,141,239,0.12)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><rect x=\