  "solution_html": "<div class=\"lc-section\"><h3 style=\"margin:0 0 12px 0;color:var(--lc-success);\">✅ 完整解法</h3><pre style=\"background:rgba(0,0,0,0.05);padding:12px;border-radius:8px;overflow-x:auto;line-height:1.5;\"><code class=\"language-python\">def rotate(matrix):\n    n = len(matrix)\n\n    # 步驟一：轉置矩陣（沿主對角線交換 matrix[i][j] 與 matrix[j][i]）\n    # 只遍歷上三角（j > i）以避免將同一對元素交換兩次\n    for i in range(n):\n        for j in range(i + 1, n):\n            matrix[i][j], matrix[j][i] = matrix[j][i], matrix[i][j]\n\n    # 步驟二：翻轉每一列（左右對調，等同沿垂直中心鏡像）\n    for i in range(n):\n        matrix[i].reverse()\n</code></pre><h4 style=\"margin:16px 0 8px 0;color:var(--lc-primary);\">📖 程式碼走查（Example 1）</h4><svg viewBox=\"0 0 600 200\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:8px 0;\"><text x=\"10\" y=\"16\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"700\">輸入: [[1,2,3],[4,5,6],[7,8,9]]</text><text x=\"10\" y=\"35\" fill=\"var(--lc-primary)\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"700\">轉置後</text><rect x=\"5\" y=\"40\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"rgba(91,141,239,0.15)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><rect x=\"41\" y=\"40\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"rgba(91,141,239,0.1)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><rect x=\"77\" y=\"40\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"rgba(91,141,239,0.05)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><rect x=\"5\" y=\"76\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"rgba(91,141,239,0.15)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><rect x=\"41\" y=\"76\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"rgba(91,141,239,0.1)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><rect x=\"77\" y=\"76\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"rgba(91,141,239,0.05)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><rect x=\"5\" y=\"112\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"rgba(91,141,239,0.15)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><rect x=\"41\" y=\"112\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"rgba(91,141,239,0.1)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><rect x=\"77\" y=\"112\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"rgba(91,141,239,0.05)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><text x=\"23\" y=\"63\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">1</text><text x=\"59\" y=\"63\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">4</text><text x=\"95\" y=\"63\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">7</text><text x=\"23\" y=\"99\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">2</text><text x=\"59\" y=\"99\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">5</text><text x=\"95\" y=\"99\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">8</text><text x=\"23\" y=\"135\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">3</text><text x=\"59\" y=\"135\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">6</text><text x=\"95\" y=\"135\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">9</text><line x1=\"118\" y1=\"90\" x2=\"148\" y2=\"90\" stroke=\"var(--lc-warning)\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><polygon points=\"148,86 156,90 148,94\" fill=\"var(--lc-warning)\"/><text x=\"137\" y=\"80\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-warning)\" font-size=\"10\">各列</text><text x=\"137\" y=\"68\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-warning)\" font-size=\"10\">翻轉</text><text x=\"224\" y=\"35\" fill=\"var(--lc-success)\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"700\">翻轉後（最終）</text><rect x=\"162\" y=\"40\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"rgba(63,185,80,0.2)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-success)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><rect x=\"198\" y=\"40\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"rgba(63,185,80,0.13)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-success)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><rect x=\"234\" y=\"40\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"rgba(63,185,80,0.06)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-success)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><rect x=\"162\" y=\"76\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"rgba(63,185,80,0.2)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-success)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><rect x=\"198\" y=\"76\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"rgba(63,185,80,0.13)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-success)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><rect x=\"234\" y=\"76\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"rgba(63,185,80,0.06)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-success)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><rect x=\"162\" y=\"112\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"rgba(63,185,80,0.2)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-success)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><rect x=\"198\" y=\"112\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"rgba(63,185,80,0.13)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-success)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><rect x=\"234\" y=\"112\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"rgba(63,185,80,0.06)\" stroke=\"var(--lc-success)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><text x=\"180\" y=\"63\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">7</text><text x=\"216\" y=\"63\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">4</text><text x=\"252\" y=\"63\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">1</text><text x=\"180\" y=\"99\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">8</text><text x=\"216\" y=\"99\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">5</text><text x=\"252\" y=\"99\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">2</text><text x=\"180\" y=\"135\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">9</text><text x=\"216\" y=\"135\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">6</text><text x=\"252\" y=\"135\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">3</text><text x=\"300\" y=\"52\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"700\">步驟一交換明細：</text><text x=\"300\" y=\"72\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"11\">(0,1)↔(1,0): 2↔4</text><text x=\"300\" y=\"90\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"11\">(0,2)↔(2,0): 3↔7</text><text x=\"300\" y=\"108\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"11\">(1,2)↔(2,1): 6↔8</text><text x=\"300\" y=\"132\" fill=\"var(--lc-success)\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"700\">步驟二各列翻轉：</text><text x=\"300\" y=\"150\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"11\">[1,4,7]→[7,4,1]</text><text x=\"300\" y=\"168\" fill=\"var(--lc-text)\" font-size=\"11\">[2,5,8]→[8,5,2] ...</text></svg><h4 style=\"margin:16px 0 8px 0;color:var(--lc-primary);\">⏱️ 複雜度分析</h4><table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:8px 0;\"><tr style=\"background:rgba(91,141,239,0.1);\"><th style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid var(--lc-border);text-align:left;\">指標</th><th style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid var(--lc-border);text-align:left;\">複雜度</th><th style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid var(--lc-border);text-align:left;\">原因</th></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid var(--lc-border);\"><strong>時間</strong></td><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid var(--lc-border);\"><code>O(n²)</code></td><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid var(--lc-border);\">轉置需遍歷上三角 n(n-1)/2 對，翻轉需遍歷 n²/2 個元素，總計 O(n²)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid var(--lc-border);\"><strong>空間</strong></td><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid var(--lc-border);\"><code>O(1)</code></td><td style=\"padding:8px;border:1px solid var(--lc-border);\">所有操作就地完成，只用到常數個暫存變數</td></tr></table><div style=\"background:rgba(255,200,0,0.12);padding:14px;border-radius:8px;border-left:4px solid var(--lc-warning);margin:16px 0;\"><strong>💡 Key Insight</strong><br><span style=\"line-height:1.6;\">順時針旋轉 90° = 先沿主對角線鏡像（轉置），再沿垂直中心鏡像（各列翻轉）。兩個就地操作串接，總空間 O(1)，完全不需要額外矩陣。</span></div></div>"
